flowRoot.flowPara: You have asked, so I must tell. The true name of the Hellion known by some as the Soul Catcher, and by others as the Master of Worms, is El'Azabat. This creature has great wisdom and hungers for the souls of men, though in truth it must be one of the least of its kind, for it has no great power.
I have found that, with care, I can control the creature long enough to extract useful information from it, for surely its knowledge is encylopædic.

It clearly lacks the deviousness of most of its kith and is no great trickster. It can be bribed with riches, as it has a thirst for gold that can easily be used against it. It also loves honey and raw meat, which you may find useful if you choose to summon it. However I implore you not to do so, even with such a low example of its species
